nodes.text: This unidentified planet was a planet located in the Outer Rim Territories.

This planet housed a Corellian settlement. At some point, the planet was taken over by Bo-Dum and Rarsk, two minor Hutt crime lords who had been evicted from the Hutt Cartel. Following the murder of their sheriff, the Corellian settlers remained at the mercy of the two Hutts, until the smuggler Han Solo and his co-pilot Chewbacca intervened.
